{"id": 1750, "genre": 1000, "title": "喜欢的小说要被改成影视剧，你最关心的问题是？", "description": "放过我最爱的那部小说就行！（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 16867, "comment_count": 80, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170621154553isI31g4q69LWtcw0.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-22T17:00:34Z", "questions": [{"id": 2471, "title": "喜欢的小说要被改成影视剧，你最关心的问题是？", "content": "喜欢的小说要被改成影视剧，你最关心的问题是？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 214855, "content": "先看版权被谁买走了，如果是口碑不好的影视公司就不抱什么希望了", "image": "img/option/option/20170621163726bSeNxf2hnw0rZqoK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 214856, "content": "希望剧情能够忠实原著，不要为了迎合观众口味改故事走向", "image": "img/option/option/201706211641084VtbsxrFKCLjJZg6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 214858, "content": "篇幅不长的小说改成电视剧的时候不要为了凑剧集注入大段无聊情节", "image": "img/option/option/20170621164852zos4iveyrOtBSw1U.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 214866, "content": "注意补充必要的背景和解释信息，让没看过小说的人也看得懂", "image": "img/option/option/20170622122907DdokEK1LaxPZGqFj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 214870, "content": "要把科幻小说变成电影，特技水平达得到吗？", "image": "img/option/option/20170621171734OAchpsRJwX9NFy76.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 214883, "content": "布景也要走点心，小说里震撼人心的场景别打折", "image": "img/option/option/20170621172106A9k8ye4Ec7U2KrO0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 214891, "content": "第一个念头就是：各大角色选的是哪些演员？", "image": "img/option/option/20170621172447U4WRQc3AybuEIfVi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 214894, "content": "想知道原著作者在改编的过程中参与多少", "image": "img/option/option/20170621172624jYaBLUXwn1k3mHb6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}